defaultA. Overcome the political difficulty of Somerset Tax payers fundin
defaultg a service for Dorset residents”.
defaultB. Persuade Somerset and Dorset County Councils to provide funds …..”
defaultThe implications
defaultI sought to use the freedom of information act to ascertain if indeed Dorset had ever paid for the service to enter the Dorset area. The answer was no. 
defaultI have been in constant communication with an officer working for the Somerset County Council. More det
defaultails to follow. 
