defaultSince the report has been written the buses that did run in Drimpton have been reduced to one bus only and that goes from Drimpton to 
defaultBridport on a Wednesday only. The Purchase of advance rail tickets from the station office have been increased by 11% to encourage people to use the internet. I imagine the same rule still applies, that is if the station office sells less than 12 tickets a
default day it will be closed. 
